

ip routing
ipv6 unicast-routing


Interface gigabitEthernet 1/0/1
no switchport
Ip address 10.0.1.251 255.255.255.0
ipv6 add 2025:ba1:3000:1::251/64
ipv6 ospf 123 area 0
ipv6 add fe80::1 link-local 
No shut 
exit 

