OSPF  IPV4
---------------------------------

router ospf 123
Router-id 1.1.1.1
Network 10.0.1.0  0.0.0.255  area 0
Network 10.0.2.0  0.0.0.255  area 0
Network 10.0.11.0 0.0.0.255 area 1 
Network 10.0.12.0 0.0.0.255 area 1


